            "id": 5890255,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 美達科技(6735)大漲7.6%，報69.4元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美達科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6735:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6735\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6735-TW</a>)10日09:21股價上漲4.9元，報69.4元，漲幅7.6%，成交222張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美達科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6735:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6735\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6735-TW</a>)所屬產業為其他電子業，主要業務為半導體之類比暨混合訊號積體電路測試儀器。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲12.57%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.03%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+4 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+3 張</li> <li>融資增減：+36 張</li> <li>融券增減：+5 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5890255",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 09:21:20",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
